data.description: Nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, this Immerian Ranch-style house exudes timeless charm and modern comfort. Boasting five bedrooms, one of which can easily transform into a stylish office space, this residence offers versatility to suit your lifestyle. The ranch-style architecture lends an inviting aura, while the lush backyard creates a haven of relaxation. The interior is a harmonious blend of functionality and elegance, featuring four bathrooms for utmost convenience. The spacious living areas showcase an open layout, seamlessly connecting the well-appointed kitchen, dining, and living spaces. Perfect for entertaining, the residence also surprises with a sleek wet bar, providing a touch of sophistication for social gatherings. The master bedroom is a retreat within itself, featuring a luxurious 5-piece master bath, offering a serene escape after a long day. Each room is bathed in natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere throughout. The thoughtful design extends to practical amenities such as air conditioning, ensuring comfort year-round. Outside, the backyard unfolds into a private oasis, inviting you to unwind amidst nature's beauty. Whether hosting a barbecue or enjoying a quiet evening, this outdoor space is a canvas for your imagination. Welcome to a home where style, comfort, and tranquility converge seamlessly. Owner will have carpets stretched and cleaned before closing
